OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to Barnsley man
OL,4,Ckilled in crash as police make fifth
OL,5,Carrest
OL,7,FThe family of a 45-year-old man who
OL,8,Fdied in Barnsley after being hit by a
OL,9,Fcar have paid tribute to him.
OL,11,FLiam Green died just before 5pm on
OL,12,FFriday 3 April in the Cudworth area of
OL,13,FBarnsley after emergency services were
OL,14,Fcalled to reports of a pedestrian
OL,15,Fbeing hit by a white Volkswagen in
OL,16,FRose Tree Avenue.
OL,18,FHis family paid tribute to him saying:
OL,19,F"We hope you're at peace now.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36702
