OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1775653862
OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to Barnsley man
OL,4,Ckilled in crash as police make fifth
OL,5,Carrest
OL,7,F"We all love you very much, sending
OL,8,Fyou big hugs from your mam, sons,
OL,9,Fbrother and family."
OL,11,FSouth Yorkshire Police say his family
OL,12,Fare being looked after by their
OL,13,Fofficers.
OL,15,FA 53-year-old man was arrested on
OL,16,Fsuspicion of murder on 5 April and is
OL,17,Fin police custody.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
