OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1775653862
OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to Barnsley man
OL,4,Ckilled in crash as police make fifth
OL,5,Carrest
OL,7,FA 33-year-old man and a 17-year-old
OL,8,Fboy were arrested on Saturday 4 April
OL,9,Fon suspicion of murder and have both
OL,10,Fbeen released on bail.
OL,12,FA 60-year-old man and a 38-year-old
OL,13,Fwoman were arrested Friday 3 April on
OL,14,Fsuspicion of murder. They remain in
OL,15,Fpolice custody.
OL,17,FA police spokesperson said: "Enquiries
OL,18,Fare ongoing and officers are appealing
OL,19,Ffor anyone with information which
OL,20,Fcould assist them with the
OL,21,Finvestigation to come forward."
